{"tid":1701083,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［行動post］我哋就係知道你哋唔敢罷工","createTime":"2019-11-08T23:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T06:51:27.000Z","uid":41366,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3a00d06a43895ff5947f8def89be3bf77fd30da5","tid":1701083,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T23:49:34.000Z","msg":"所以無論如何今日同聽日一定會盡量爆鐵<br />\n知唔知點解要咁做<br />\n係因為你哋和你非有太多包袱所以唔敢罷工<br />\n我哋明你哋嘅感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以今日聽日無論如何都會出嚟爆地鐵幫你地一把<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等你哋有藉口可以被罷工<br />\n你諗下一眾死去既義士，佢得到嘅係乜嘢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>[black]<span style=\"color: red;\">係乜撚都冇</span>[/black]</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解你地仲未肯出黎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔介意你地join支線活動，咩搞美心，搞優品，小弟都好贊成<br />\n但你地可唔可以都join埋主線活動，我唔求你地馬上即刻變成超級勇武<br />\n但可唔可以做前線既盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴晚果班仆街狗，拉晒議員，阻住救護員進行天職，仲要係民居到看，二惡英，毒害香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔相信你地會有報應<br />\n但我相信好快就會有復仇嘅火魔法係你身上展現，呢樣係我哋短期可以為死去嘅義士可以做嘅獻祭方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n爆鐵位置<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大埔<br />\n沙田<br />\n大圍<br />\n油塘<br />\n觀塘<br />\n黃大仙<br />\n太子<br />\n旺角<br />\n油麻地<br />\n灣仔<br />\n荃灣<br />\n葵芳</span><br />\n時間係收車前一個鐘，玩一玩快閃<br />\n要所有閘機都total loss<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再配合雙11既黎明行動，我地要嚴重打擊香港經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c081c7968ea501cb0fe139d3734dbe6594430101","tid":1701083,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T23:51:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e351758775c83f6932d8b907de31a2f68271014","tid":1701083,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T23:52:54.000Z","msg":"出黎呀，香港人"},{"pid":"4d3ce6400d3c481e828e419d8aa028a9c33e6d5c","tid":1701083,"uid":122915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T23:53:13.000Z","msg":"我提醒<br />\n大埔林村個到迥旋處一塞<br />\n係可以塞埋粉嶺上水個D過黎大埔既人<br />\n而村入面本身出九龍個D都要經個位先上到高速<br />\n雖然無市區咁多人 但個個位求奇一塞唔搞返個幾鐘都走唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7687a3fcb79ee4d264f97ce89cf12b4806c1acb8","tid":1701083,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T23:53:13.000Z","msg":"罷工前哨戰呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6333894e013770c655d65d7aad1774c9c73f3379","tid":1701083,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T23:55:06.000Z","msg":"香港人，覺醒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"